                                                    skos:definition "A BZK compensation office role is inherited by governmental offices, which is realised when a BZK applicant applies for compensation for at least one persecuted person and the office claims a BZK card."@en .


###  https://bzk.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/BZK_0010002
<https://bzk.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/BZK_0010002> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                    rdfs:subClassOf <https://nfdi.fiz-karlsruhe.de/ontology/NFDI_0000229> ,
